\`v-slot\` is rejected with \"not supported yet\". Slot contracts via \`defineSlot()\` exist, but there's no way to render slot content in templates.

## Expected

```html
<MyLayout>
  <template v-slot:header>
    <h1>Title</h1>
  </template>
  <template v-slot:default>
    <p>Content</p>
  </template>
</MyLayout>
```